00:41:03.901 --> 00:41:06.620 position:19.52%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>on a novel here, Jake.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1056
00:41:06.620 --> 00:41:09.940 position:19.52%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The dialogue is sharp,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1057
00:41:06.620 --> 00:41:09.940 position:19.52%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
