1071
00:41:32.373 --> 00:41:34.932 position:50.00%,start align:start size:40.48% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But she got them</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1072
00:41:32.373 --> 00:41:34.932 position:50.00%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
